# Prettier mangles MkDocs admonition syntax — every `!!! note "..."` block
# requires its content to be 4-space-indented, and prettier strips that
# indent. The docs auto-update workflow then re-adds the indent on next
# merge, kicking off an endless lint-vs-docs churn cycle that blocks
# unrelated PRs. user_docs/ is rendered by mkdocs (see mkdocs.yml), not
# by anything that needs prettier's normalization.
user_docs/
